{"tid":1031353,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 收到推銷電話點先可以一招收佢皮？","createTime":"2019-02-21T14:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T14:59:04.000Z","uid":10390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a27695859764fce388917686def2b48527361271","tid":1031353,"uid":10390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我約8年前開始用依家呢個電話號碼 一開始用已經間唔時會有電話打黎搵姓劉嘅人<br />\n有時係「你好，唔該想該劉生」 有時係「你好，你係咪劉小姐啊？」<br />\n一開始我都係同佢講打錯 但佢地一聽到就CUT我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但過兩日又打過黎 (唔同座機 例如第一日係2345 1234 第二日就係2345 2234咁樣)<br />\n後來呢啲電話愈黎愈頻密 仲要cut佢線都繼續打黎 由於之前係連登睇過人地話如果有唔識嘅電話係咁打黎 有機會係屋企人入左醫院 醫院打比你 所以我後來就唔cut 選擇同佢地講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事實證明係無撚用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「你好，唔該劉生」<br />\n「姓劉呢家人轉左電話好耐架喇⋯請你唔好再打⋯」<br />\n「嘟⋯嘟⋯嘟⋯」<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家唯有聽一次block一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好煩 講到呢度我只係想乞個解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (除左轉電話號碼)"},{"pid":"7abd5866b6bb7718daed9e3858ba3117058eba2e","tid":1031353,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:56:44.000Z","msg":"小熊啦"},{"pid":"b69d68af663d1f77810092c8b3389836fccda889","tid":1031353,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:59:04.000Z","msg":"你喜歡做愛嗎？"}]}